<p>We can easily removed local untracked files from the current git working tree by using below git comments.</p>

<pre><code>git reset [--soft | --mixed [-N] | --hard | --merge | --keep] [-q] [&lt;commit&gt;]
</code></pre>

<p><strong>Example:</strong></p>

<pre><code>git reset --hard HEAD
</code></pre>

